                "reaction": {
                  "code": "94-PU-240(N,F)42-MO-99,CUM,FY,,FST",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "94-PU-240(N,F)42-MO-99,CUM,FY,,FST",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "94-PU-240(N,F)42-MO-99",
                        "target": "94-PU-240",
                        "projectile": "N",
                        "process": "F",
                        "product": "42-MO-99",
                        "quantity": "CUM,FY",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": "FST",
                        "quantity_236": "CUM,FY"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Relative yields determined as a ratio to that of Mo-99,",
                "and the ratios for each product were averaged over all",
                "the experiments. The number of fissions in the Pu-240",
                "targets was calculated from the masses of the Pu-240",
                "and U-235 monitor foils, the fission cross section",
                "ratio Pu-240/U-235 was taken as 0.825 +/- 5%. The",
                "absolute yield of Mo-99 determined in this manner was",
                "0.0636 +/- 0.0038 atoms/fission.",
                "The number of fissions was also calculated by the",
                "requirement of unit total yield in each half of the",
                "mass-yield distribution. This method gave a yield of",
                "0.0600 +/- 0.0030 atoms/fission for Mo-99.",
                "The average of the results from these two methods,",
                "0.0618 atoms/fission, for the yield of Mo-99, was used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Three four-hour irradiations. Disintegration",
                " rates of fission products determined with gamma-ray",
                " spectrometry and/or beta-particle assay. Pu-240",
                " content of target determined by mass spectrometry.",
                " Delay in analysis precludes measurements of half-lives",
                " less than ten hours. Number of fissions determined as",
                " average of two methods:",
                " .cross section ratio of Pu-240/U-235 and average",
                "  number of U-235 fissions.",
                " .summing up each half of mass yield curve."
              ]
            }
          ],
